			<img alt='' src='http://1.gravatar.com/avatar/74149d915a02cf32bdd3b1a1c155dfd5?s=32&amp;d=monsterid&amp;r=G' class='avatar avatar-32 photo' height='32' width='32' />			<cite class="fn">Надежда</cite><span class="says">:</span>		</div>
		
