			<img alt='' src='http://1.gravatar.com/avatar/b2cff8d31c6ddf90f6b3b5efee404121?s=32&amp;d=monsterid&amp;r=G' class='avatar avatar-32 photo' height='32' width='32' />			<cite class="fn">рашид</cite><span class="says">:</span>		</div>
		
